sorcer.core.proxy

Interface Partner

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Administrable, Outer, Service
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GroupManagement, RemotePartner
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccountProvider, ExertMonitor, ServiceCataloger, ServiceConcatenator, ServiceJobber, ServiceProvider, ServiceSpacer, ServiceTasker, StaticServiceProvider

    public interface Partner
extends Outer, Service
    Servers and other compound proxies using inner proxies to extend their functionalty via calls on the inner proxies implement this interface. To provide service-to-service functionality this interface extends Service.
    Author:
    Mike Sobolewski
